    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="847822473">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-847822473" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-847822473" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="847822473">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sarmusliu/">萨缪</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-09-24</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">还真是“讲”稿。读惯孟森明史讲义还是多少不太适应。个别专题还是不错。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="767804295">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-767804295" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-767804295" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="767804295">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/geoff/">東寫西讀</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2014-01-31</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">《明史讲稿》是樊树志先生2010年在上海企业家读书会主讲明史的一部讲稿，不同于专题论文，讲稿更多的是引领学生入门，必须兼顾基本知识点，把该领域最权威观点介绍给听众，当然还要加上自家独到之见，否则就成文抄公了。治史有专家和通家两种途径，小处见大是专家之学，博洽周瞻是通人治学</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="996926968">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-996926968" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-996926968" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="996926968">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/g9421/">g9421</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-01-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">介绍并融合了现当代海内外明史研究的很多成果，贸易、御倭、援朝、东林等观点有独到见地。但囿于讲稿体例，史料考证和专题选择上不甚周详，一些人物臧否有臆断之嫌。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="820407033">
        <div class="comment">
